  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Removing the horns of wild rhinos leaves them defenseless.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[It takes years for horns to regrow.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[Some say removing the horns will keep poachers from killing rhinos.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Unfortunately, there is little to back up this position.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Poachers have been known to kill rhinos out of anger or simple meanness.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6" implicit="true"><![CDATA[No, the horn of rhinos should not be removed to prevent them from being poached.]]></edu>
